It blasts internally stored sand
from ports on its body to create
a towering twister for attack.

Its huge mouth is almost seven
feet across. It has enough power
to completely crush a car.

It is surprisingly quick to anger.
It holds its mouth agape as a
display of its strength.

It brandishes its gaping mouth in a
display of fearsome strength. It raises
vast quantities of sand while attacking.

Il prend grand soin des Crabicoque,
car ils laident  se dbarrasser des cailloux
qui obstruent parfois les orifices de son corps.

Manchmal bleiben in den ffnungen in seinem

Protege con celo a los Dwebble, ya que le
ayudan a liberarse de las piedras que a veces

Protegge con zelo i Dwebble, perch lo aiutano

Stones can get stuck in the ports on their bodies.
Dwebble help dislodge such stones, so
Hippowdon look after these Pokmon.

Il entre dans une violente colre quand
on lnerve : il expulse le sable quil a accumul
pour provoquer de vritables temptes.

Wenn man es wtend macht, wird es rabiat. Es
stt aufgenommenen Sand aus und verursacht
damit einen Sandsturm.

Puede ser muy agresivo cuando se enfada.
Provoca autnticas tempestades de arena al
expeler la que ha tragado.

Quando si arrabbia diventa molto violento
ed espelle la sabbia che ha immagazzinato
provocando tempeste di sabbia.

When roused to violence by its rage, it spews out
the quantities of sand it has swallowed and
whips up a sandstorm.
